 {"id":"bd-1sf.9","title":"Validate production web app route and same-data continuity contract","description":"Identify the correct publicly accessible web app URL for Agent Mail, verify route availability, and define how the hero CTA leads to the real web app experience using the same underlying dataset context.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-05T05:59:13.949420125Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-05T07:02:29.361224478Z","closed_at":"2026-03-05T07:02:29.361206144Z","close_reason":"VALIDATED: Production web app route is /showcase (https://mcpagentmail.com/showcase). heroTuiDemo.realWebAppUrl already points there via siteConfig.url+/showcase. No separate web app exists - Agent Mail is a Rust CLI tool. Data continuity: heroTuiDemo uses hardcoded snapshot data (not live SQLite). Same-data contract: the showcase route renders interactive viz components independent of hero data, so no cross-route data sync is needed.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1sf.9","depends_on_id":"bd-1sf","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-05T17:10:49Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":9,"issue_id":"bd-1sf.9","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"Known current state from probes: https://mcpagentmail.com/mail responds 404, root https://mcpagentmail.com responds 200. Need to identify/establish the correct public web-app route for CTA and same-data continuity before implementation.","created_at":"2026-03-05T06:04:02Z"}]}
